description:
[English]
Orginial by Christopher Tin, Remastered by Sean.M, and vocal and choir by beloved HatsuneMiku

always tring to experiment the potential of Miku doing the choir, so here we are

Artwork also by me too, hope you like it

Sean.M

[中文]
原曲原作者為田志仁，親王重新改編，並且將人聲合唱部分以初音歌聲取代
一直想嘗試初音的合唱潛能，所以就做了，包括曲子的封面也是自己畫的，希望您喜歡

親王
